{"tid":2160493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿學生會通過登蘋果頭版廣告 兩名學生會評議會成員辭任並獲接納","createTime":"2020-08-17T03:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T14:32:57.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"120bfbd114f6d3ae2e2e35e474c7f3f5d67c26fe","tid":2160493,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T03:55:34.000Z","msg":"香港大學學生會，昨日（16 日）在《蘋果日報》頭版刊登題為「致香港人：願我們以生命回報自由」的聲明書，據港大學苑報道，兩名學生會評議會成員，文化聯會會長朱卓楠及評議會文化聯會代表二陳穎亨，因不滿評議會通過撥款在《蘋果》登廣告，辭任評議會並獲接納。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%96%BC%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E9%A0%AD%E7%89%88%E5%88%8A%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E5%AD%B8%E8%8B%91-%E5%85%A9%E8%A9%95%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E8%AB%8B%E8%BE%AD-%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E6%9C%89%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25BC%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%2588%258A%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%258B%2591-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25BE%25AD-%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=389326a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25BC%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%2588%258A%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%258B%2591-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E8%25AB